00:22:39.800 --> 00:22:41.600
Ayolah, mungkin saja dia orang baik!

00:22:41.600 --> 00:22:43.820
Dia ditangkap karena dia orang jahat!

00:22:43.820 --> 00:22:46.980
Tidak! Mustahil, mustahil, mustahil!
Sangat mu…

00:22:47.790 --> 00:22:50.110
